    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 18-02-2025</p>

<p>Welcome to <strong>easternwordsmith.com</strong> (the “Website”). Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our Website.</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<p>We collect different types of information to improve our services and provide a better user experience. This includes:</p>

<h3>A. Automatically Collected Data</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> Your IP address, browser type, pages visited, time spent on pages, and other statistics collected via Google Analytics.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small files stored on your device to enhance your browsing experience.</li>
</ul>

<h3>B. Third-Party Services</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Tracks website usage data to analyze traffic and improve content.</li>
    <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> Uses cookies to display personalized ads based on your browsing history.</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

<p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Improve website functionality and user experience.</li>
    <li>Analyze visitor behavior to optimize content.</li>
    <li>Display relevant ads using Google AdSense.</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>3. Third-Party Advertisements</h2>

<p>Our Website uses <strong>Google AdSense</strong>, which may place third-party cookies in your browser. Google and its partners may use these cookies to display personalized ads.</p>

<p><strong>How to Opt-Out of Personalized Ads:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Visit <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a> to control ad preferences.</li>
    <li>Use browser settings to disable cookies (note that this may affect website functionality).</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>4. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>

<p>Cookies help us enhance your experience. You can disable cookies via your browser settings, but this may affect certain website features.</p>

<h3>Managing Cookies:</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Google Chrome:</strong> Settings > Privacy & Security > Cookies and Site Data</li>
    <li><strong>Mozilla Firefox:</strong> Options > Privacy & Security > Cookies and Site Data</li>
    <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences > Privacy</li>
</ul>

<p>For more details, visit <a href="https://www.allaboutcookies.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">All About Cookies</a>.</p>

<hr>

<h2>5. Data Protection & Security</h2>

<p>We take security seriously and implement measures to protect your personal data. However, no online transmission is 100% secure, so we encourage caution when sharing personal information.</p>

<hr>


<h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>

<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, so please review it periodically.</p>

